title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Zwraca arcus cosinus (w radianach) danej liczby.</p>\n\n<p><math display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo>∀</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>∊</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>,</mo><mspace width=\"thickmathspace\"></mspace><mstyle mathvariant=\"monospace\"><mrow><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"thinmathspace\">Math.acos</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle><mo>=</mo><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">arccos</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mtext> the unique </mtext><mspace width=\"thickmathspace\"></mspace><mi>y</mi><mo>∊</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>;</mo><mi>π</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace><mtext>such that</mtext><mspace width=\"thickmathspace\"></mspace><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">cos</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"TeX\">\\forall x \\in [{-1};1],\\;\\mathtt{\\operatorname{Math.acos}(x)} = \\arccos(x) = \\text{ the unique } \\; y \\in [0; \\pi] \\, \\text{such that} \\; \\cos(y) = x</annotation></semantics></math></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>Math.acos(<var>x</var>)</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"x\"><code>x</code>&nbsp;</dt>\n <dd>liczba.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Metoda <code>acos</code> zwraca wartość numeryczną od 0 do pi dla <code>x</code> pomiędzy -1 a 1. Jeśli liczba <code>x</code> jest spoza przedziału [-1, 1], zwracany jest <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p>Ponieważ <code>acos</code> jest statyczną metodą obiektu <code>Math</code>, zawsze odwołujemy się do niej poprzez <code>Math.acos()</code>, a nie jak do metody instancji obiektu <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math\"><code>Math</code></a> utworzonej przez użytkownika.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_zastosowanie_math.acos","title":"Przykład: Zastosowanie <code>Math.acos()</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Poniższa funkcja zwraca arcus cosinus zmiennej <code>x</code>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js  language-js notranslate\"><code>Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">acos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// NaN</span>\nMath<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">acos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 3.141592653589793</span>\nMath<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">acos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// 1.5707963267948966</span>\nMath<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">acos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1.0471975511965979</span>\nMath<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">acos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// 0</span>\nMath<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">acos</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// NaN</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Jeśli do <code>getAcos</code> przekazana zostanie wartość -1, funkcja zwróci 3.141592653589793; jeśli przekazana zostanie wartość 2, zwrócony zostanie <code>NaN</code>, ponieważ 2 jest poza zakresem (tj. dziedziną funkcji arcus cosinus).</p>","titleAsText":"Przykład: Zastosowanie Math.acos()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/asin\"><code>Math.asin()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/atan\"><code>Math.atan()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/atan2\"><code>Math.atan2()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/cos\"><code>Math.cos()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/sin\"><code>Math.sin()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/tan\"><code>Math.tan()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przyk.c5.82ady"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce"}],"summary":"Zwraca arcus cosinus (w radianach) danej liczby.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Math.acos()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/math/acos","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/math/acos/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Dokumentacja referencyjna JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Obiekty"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math","title":"Math"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/acos","title":"Math.acos()"}],"pageTitle":"Math.acos() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}